check.output:
📚 **Required Skills Loaded for Review:**
        {{#each story_required_skills}}
        - ✅ {{skill_name}} loaded (will check FORBIDDEN rules)
        {{/each}}

step.output:
**🔥 CODE REVIEW FINDINGS, {user_name}!**

      **Story:** {{story_file}}
      **SaaS Readiness Score:** {{saas_readiness_score}}/100 {{#if saas_readiness_score lt 70}}⚠️ BELOW THRESHOLD{{/if}}
      **Git vs Story Discrepancies:** {{git_discrepancy_count}} found
      **Issues Found:** {{critical_count}} Critical, {{high_count}} High, {{medium_count}} Medium, {{low_count}} Low
      **Accumulated Tech Debt:** {{tech_debt_count}} pending items

      {{#each severity_levels}}
      ## {{icon}} {{label}} ISSUES
      {{#each issues}}
      - **[{{severity}}][{{dimension}}]** {{description}}
        📍 {{file}}:{{line}}
        🔧 修復方案: {{fix_suggestion}}
      {{/each}}
      {{/each}}

check.action:
Auto-fix ALL CRITICAL issues:
        - Read each file → Apply fix_suggestion → Verify
        - Update {{fixed_count}}

check.output:
🚨 **架構 Bug 偵測！以下問題必須修復，不可延後：**
        {{#each architecture_bugs}}
        - [{{severity}}] {{description}} [{{file}}:{{line}}]
        {{/each}}

        根據 CLAUDE.md §1.4 規範，這些不是「設計選擇」而是「架構 Bug」。

check.action:
For EACH issue in {{deferred_issues}}, perform analysis:
        **A. 根因分析**: root_cause_category + detail (2-3 句因果鏈)
          Categories: CROSS_MODULE_DEPENDENCY | INFRASTRUCTURE_CHANGE | ARCHITECTURE_REDESIGN | SHARED_COMPONENT | UPSTREAM_DEPENDENCY | TESTING_GAP | DATA_MIGRATION
        **B. 路由決策** (按 MEMORY.md 規則，CR 延後項目必須留在原 Epic):
          1. 同 Epic 內既有 backlog/ready-for-dev Story（從 {{sprint_status_cache}} 查詢，不讀 Story 全文）
          2. 無匹配 → 建立新 Story key: {epic}-{next_id}-{short_desc}
        Set: {{issue.target_story_id}}, {{issue.routing_reason}}
        Store in {{analyzed_deferred_issues}}

check.output:
**✅ 技術債側車文件寫入完成**
        - 分析: {{action_count}} | 側車文件: {{unique_target_count}} 個
        - 路徑: {implementation_artifacts}/tech-debt/
        {{#each grouped_deferrals}}
        - 📄 {{target_story_id}}.debt.md ({{item_count}} items, {{max_severity}})
        {{/each}}

📋 **Skill Staleness → tech_debt_items:**
        {{#each stale_skills}}
        - SKILL_STALE | {{skill_name}} | {{severity}} (existing: {{existing_count}}) | {{matched_files}}
        {{/each}}

check.action:
Append to CR report (tech_debt_items section):
        ### Skill Staleness (SKILL_STALE)
        | Skill | Severity | Matched Files | Existing Count |
        |-------|----------|---------------|---------------|
        {{#each stale_skills}}
        | {{skill_name}} | {{severity}} | {{matched_files}} | {{existing_count}} |
        {{/each}}
        > INFO-only domain fallback entries are noted below (no DB write):
        {{#each domain_fallback_entries}}
        - ℹ️ {{skill_name}}: domain match only
        {{/each}}

step.action:
Calculate final metrics:
      {{critical_remaining}}, {{high_remaining}}, {{acs_incomplete}}
      {{final_tech_debt}} = {{tech_debt_count}} + count of new DEFERRED entries pushed in Step 4 (do NOT re-read registry.yaml)

step.output:
**✅ Code Review Complete!**
      **Story:** {{story_key}} | **Status:** {{new_status}} | **SaaS Score:** {{saas_readiness_score}}/100
      📊 Fixed: {{fixed_count}} | Deferred: {{action_count}} | Tech Debt: {{final_tech_debt}}/15
      🚧 Gates: Critical={{#if critical_remaining==0}}✅{{else}}❌{{/if}} High={{#if high_remaining==0}}✅{{else}}⚠️{{/if}} Debt={{#if final_tech_debt<=15}}✅{{else}}⚠️{{/if}} SaaS={{#if saas_readiness_score>=70}}✅{{else}}⚠️{{/if}}
      {{#if new_status=="done"}}🎉 Code review 通過！Story 可進入下一階段。
      {{else if new_status=="blocked"}}⛔ Story 被阻塞！請先修復 CRITICAL 問題。
      {{else}}📋 請處理待辦項目後，重新執行 code-review。{{#if action_count>0}} 💡 延後項目已關聯到 **{{target_story_id}}**{{/if}}
      {{/if}}

step.action:
Create review report file:
      ```markdown
      # Code Review Report: {{story_key}}
      **Review Date:** {{system_date}} | **Reviewer:** {user_name} (AI-Assisted) | **SaaS Score:** {{saas_readiness_score}}/100

      ## Summary
      | Metric | Value |
      |--------|-------|
      | Story Status | {{new_status}} |
      | Issues Found/Fixed/Deferred | {{total_issues}} / {{fixed_count}} / {{action_count}} |
      | Target Story | {{target_story_id}} |

      ## Production Gate Results
      Zero Critical: {{pass_fail}} | High Resolved: {{pass_fail}} | Debt: {{final_tech_debt}}/15 | SaaS: {{saas_readiness_score}}/70

      ## Issues by SaaS Dimension
      (Dynamic table: Security/Scalability/Observability/DataConsistency/ErrorHandling/CodeQuality × CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)

      ## Detailed Findings
      {{#each all_issues}}
      ### [{{severity}}][{{dimension}}] {{title}}
      - **File:** {{file}}:{{line}} | **Resolution:** {{#if fixed}}Fixed{{else}}Deferred → {{target_story_id}}{{/if}}
      {{/each}}

      ## Tech Debt Tracking
      {{#if action_count > 0}}延後項目已關聯到: **{{target_story_id}}**
      | 嚴重度 | 數量 | 修復期限 |
      |--------|------|---------|
      | HIGH/MEDIUM | {{count}} | 下個 Sprint |
      | LOW | {{count}} | Backlog |
      {{else}}無延後項目。{{/if}}

      ## 文檔同步狀態 (TD-31)
      {{#if cr_doc_drift_items}}
      **狀態**: ⚠️ Drift Detected

      | 受影響文檔 | 變更類型 | 嚴重度 | 觸發變更 |
      |-----------|---------|:------:|---------|
      {{#each cr_doc_drift_items}}
      | {{affected_doc}} | {{change_type}} | {{severity}} | {{changed_file}} |
      {{/each}}

      **需更新文檔清單 + 目標 Story**:
      {{#each cr_must_sync_docs}}
      - `{{doc_path}}` → Target Story: {{target_story}}
      {{/each}}
      {{else}}
      **狀態**: ✅ N/A — No documentation drift detected from CR fixes
      {{/if}}
      ```

